Class AdminStatisticTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • JFiles.Controllers.AdminStatisticTable

  • @Controller
public class AdminStatisticTable
extends java.lang.Object
    Controller for work with menu Admin->Statistic Table
    Responsible for display Statistics table content, creating new records and edit existing records
